        "heading": "Paragraphs 50–55 — Recording decisions",
        "locator": "GMC paragraphs 50–55",
        "evidence_summary": "Supports recording the exchange of information leading to a decision, the decision and action agreed, who made or agreed it, and a decision to take no action."
