        "heading": "Paragraphs 76–86 — If a patient may lack capacity",
        "locator": "GMC paragraphs 76–86",
        "evidence_summary": "Supports a time- and decision-specific capacity assessment, presumption of capacity, practical support, and recording the assessment; UK legal rules require UAE adaptation."
